  geom_line(aes(y=Wheelbase, color="Coral1")) +
  geom_line(aes(y=Rear.seat.room*max_ratio), color="Royalblue") + # Rear.seat.room max_ratio  y2  
  scale_y_continuous(sec.axis = sec_axis(~.*(max_ratio/10), name = "Rear.seat.room")) # sec_axis
